    "description": "Pugmarks India International Enterprises is actively seeking a talented and motivated Guest Relations Manager to join our dynamic team in Nashik. This is an excellent opportunity for professionals who are passionate about making a real impact in a fast-growing organization.\n\nAbout Pugmarks India International Enterprises:\nPugmarks India International Enterprises is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Develop and maintain relationships with corporate clients\n• Ensure compliance with FSSAI, health, and safety regulations\n• Monitor F&B service quality and maintain hygiene standards\n• Assist in menu planning, costing, and food festival coordination\n• Coordinate housekeeping and maintenance for room readiness\n• Conduct regular guest satisfaction surveys and implement improvements\n• Handle guest complaints and resolve issues promptly\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Diploma or Degree in Hospitality Management\n• 3-6 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Travel Management\n• Proficiency in Barista Skills\n• Proficiency in Yield Management\n• Proficiency in MICE\n• Proficiency in Opera PMS\n• Proficiency in Sommelier Skills\n• Proficiency in Housekeeping Standards\n• Proficiency in Customer Relations\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Salary Range: 7 LPA - 15 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Nashik, Maharashtra, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Pugmarks India International Enterprises!",
